<p style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size: 0.875em;">Dear {!Internal_Registration__c.Name_CN__c}</p>
<br/>
<p style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size: 0.875em;">欢迎您来青参加2025年度营销会议。青岛天气多云间晴，气温-2至9度，提醒您注意保暖。</p>
<p style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size: 0.875em;">青岛海天金融中心酒店地址：崂山区仙霞岭路29号。18、19日10:00-20:00将有工作人员在酒店大堂协助为您办理入住并发放参会证件。</p>
<br/>
<p style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size: 0.875em;">Dear {!Internal_Registration__c.Name_CN__c}</p>
<br/>
<p style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size: 0.875em;">Welcome to Qingdao for the 2025 Annual Marketing Meeting. The weather is sunny with temperatures from -2 to 9 degrees Celsius. Kindly remind you to keep warm. </p>
<p style="font-family:Times New Roman;font-size: 0.875em;">The address of the Qingdao Haitian Financial Center Hotel is: 29 Xianxialing Road, Laoshan District. On the 18th and 19th, from 10:00 to 20:00, staff will be in the hotel lobby to assist you with check-in and to distribute meeting cards.</p>